        <Parent_String>double pieces [300224812], armor by function [300210823], armor (protective wear) [300036745], protective wear [300209266], costume by function [300212133], costume (mode of fashion) [300178802], Costume (hierarchy name) [300209261], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
